3
00:00:16,568 --> 00:00:19,847
You couldn't get through
this town down there,

4
00:00:19,881 --> 00:00:22,056
but it's dead now.

5
00:00:22,091 --> 00:00:25,094
We had eight or ten coal mines
shut down at one time.

6
00:00:25,128 --> 00:00:29,063
Come on, everybody in here!
Have a seat! Let's go!

7
00:00:29,098 --> 00:00:32,273
It's the same halftime speech
every single week.

8
00:00:32,308 --> 00:00:35,587
♪

9
00:00:35,621 --> 00:00:38,452
There's so much negativity
surrounding this place

10
00:00:38,486 --> 00:00:40,626
that no one ever focuses
on the positive.

11
00:00:40,661 --> 00:00:43,215
They see us as ignorant
or hillbillies.

12
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:47,185
Overdose capital
of the East Coast.

13
00:00:47,219 --> 00:00:49,428
There's really more here
than just poverty

14
00:00:49,463 --> 00:00:50,878
and illiteracy and drugs.

15
00:00:50,912 --> 00:00:53,260
There's a lot
of good people here.

16
00:00:53,294 --> 00:00:55,745
When you walk on this field,
you better have tunnel vision.

17
00:00:55,779 --> 00:00:57,264
Don't look left.
Don't look right.

18
00:00:57,298 --> 00:00:59,093
You look at that scoreboard,

19
00:00:59,128 --> 00:01:01,268
and that shit burn in your
heart, you understand me?

20
00:01:01,302 --> 00:01:02,959
We got some ground to make up,

21
00:01:02,993 --> 00:01:05,617
but once we make that
ground up, we'll take off.

22
00:01:05,651 --> 00:01:06,756
Let's go!

23
00:01:09,448 --> 00:01:11,312
♪ I took a walk
through this ♪

24
00:01:11,347 --> 00:01:14,488
♪ Beautiful world

25
00:01:14,522 --> 00:01:19,596
♪ Felt the cool rain
on my shoulder ♪

26
00:01:19,631 --> 00:01:23,083
♪ Found something good
in this ♪

27
00:01:23,117 --> 00:01:25,844
♪ Beautiful world

28
00:01:25,878 --> 00:01:31,677
♪ I felt the rain
getting colder ♪

29
